textAfterTable: Individual Leaders  Scoring Totals  Lafayette - Homan 17  Colgate - Harris 19  Rebounds  Lafayette - Ottewill-Soulsby 10  Colgate - Harris 10  Assists  Lafayette - O'Hare 6  Colgate - Kobiela 6  Steals  Lafayette - Macklin 2  Colgate - Repoli 2  Blocks  Lafayette - Homan 3  Lehigh - Reid, Kobiela 1 Easton, Pa. - Emily Homan led four Leopards in double figures with 17 points and nine rebounds as Lafayette took down Colgate, 81-70 in Patriot League play on Wednesday night. Lafayette locked up the sixth seed in the Patriot League Tournament and will take on either Army or American in the quarterfinals next week. The Leopards improved to 14-14 overall and 8-9 in Patriot League play and Colgate dropped to 3-14 in league play. Jamie O'Hare knocked down four threes on her way to 14 points,
